se.cbb.jprime.io

Class PrIMENewickTreeVerifier

  • java.lang.Object
    • se.cbb.jprime.io.PrIMENewickTreeVerifier

  • public class PrIMENewickTreeVerifier
extends java.lang.Object
    Collects a number of sanity checks and similar for a PrIMENewickTree, e.g. that all leaves have names, ultrametricity property on times, etc.

    Either invoke static method runStandardTestSuite() or create an instance and run individual tests.

      • validateUltrametricity

        public void validateUltrametricity(boolean reqZeroAtleaves,
                          boolean reqCompatibility)
                            throws NewickIOException
        Verifies that vertex times are either empty or ultrametric, and similarly that arc times are either empty or ultrametric. Numeric precision discrepancies are allowed up to the value of constant MAX_TIME_DIFF.
        Parameters:
        reqZeroAtleaves - true to require that all leaf times equal 0.
        reqCompatibility - true to require that vertex times, arc times and tree top time are compatible.
        Throws:
        NewickIOException - if incorrect.
